# DSL chemistry NVDA speech dictionary. Copy or append these entries to default.dic.
# Columns: pattern, replacement, caseSensitive, type. Type 1 means regular expression.
# standalone parentheses — default TTS/NVDA skip "(" and ")" unless spoken explicitly
(	 open parenthesis 	0	0
)	 close parenthesis 	0	0
# multiplication sign (unicode times and cross variants from Google Docs / LMS)
×	 times 	0	0
✕	 times 	0	0
# full phrase with heat capacity unit
Effective heat capacity (J/°C)	Effective heat capacity in jools per degree Celsius	0	0
# parenthetical heat capacity unit
\(J/°C\)	in jools per degree Celsius	0	1
# heat capacity unit
J/°C	jools per degree Celsius	0	0
# heat capacity unit with optional spaces around slash
J\s?/\s?°C	jools per degree Celsius	0	1
# heat capacity unit after a number with optional spaces
(?<=\d)\s?J\s?/\s?°C	jools per degree Celsius	0	1
# specific heat capacity unit
J/g°C	jools per gram degree Celsius	0	0
# specific heat capacity unit with space
J/g °C	jools per gram degree Celsius	0	0
# specific heat capacity unit with spaced slash
J / g°C	jools per gram degree Celsius	0	0
# specific heat capacity unit with spaced slash and degree
J / g °C	jools per gram degree Celsius	0	0
# specific heat capacity unit with parentheses and multiplication dot
J/(g·°C)	jools per gram degree Celsius	0	0
# specific heat capacity unit with optional spaces around slash
J\s?/\s?g\s?°C	jools per gram degree Celsius	0	1
# specific heat capacity unit after a number with optional spaces
(?<=\d)\s?J\s?/\s?g\s?°C	jools per gram degree Celsius	0	1
# parenthetical specific heat capacity unit
\(J/g°C\)	open parenthesis jools per gram degree Celsius close parenthesis	0	1
# parenthetical specific heat capacity unit with space
\(J/g °C\)	open parenthesis jools per gram degree Celsius close parenthesis	0	1
# parenthetical specific heat capacity unit with spaced slash
\(J / g°C\)	open parenthesis jools per gram degree Celsius close parenthesis	0	1
# energy per gram unit
J/g	jools per gram	0	0
# energy per gram unit with optional spaces around slash
J\s?/\s?g\b	jools per gram	0	1
# molar mass unit
g/mol	grams per mol	0	0
# molar mass unit with optional spaces around slash
g\s?/\s?mol	grams per mol	0	1
# molar energy unit, phonetic reading
kJ/mol	killuh jools per mol	0	0
# molar energy unit with optional spaces around slash
kJ\s?/\s?mol	killuh jools per mol	0	1
# molar energy unit
J/mol	jools per mol	0	0
# molar energy unit with optional spaces around slash
J\s?/\s?mol	jools per mol	0	1
